  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supply Chain Transformation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The areas of focus on supply chain transformation are: finalisation of the set-up of the new structure (, systems re-development (revamping our standard list system, linking our procurement systems to the Management Information System &#x2013; MIS). This has already started and systems specs are being developed. System rebuild is scheduled for July/August and user testing anticipated taking place around September/October. The aim is to complete roll out the revamped supply chain system (standard list is the platform) by end of 2019.</narrative>
  </description>
